    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 115.</p><p>Reality Slash</p><p>Strike, Zulfiqar</p><p>Weapon: Any slashing melee weapon Classes: Barbarian, Fighter, Ranger Channeling Time: 1 action Base LP Cost: 0 LP Range: 300-foot long, 5-foot wide line / 90-foot cone Duration: Instantaneous</p><p>You perform an attack so powerful it cuts through reality itself. You can shape this attack as a 300-footlong, 5-foot-wide line or as a 90-foot cone. Each creature in the area must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking 15d6 Lethal damage on a failed save, or half as much on a successful one. This attack affects creatures and objects in the ethereal plane.</p><p>LP Cost. You can use this Mythical Technique at the end of another creature’s turn by expending 1 Legendary Point.</p></div>",
